WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:01.600
But what if you got the wrong person?

2
00:00:01.600 --> 00:00:03.766
There are so many people who look alike all over the world

3
00:00:03.833 --> 00:00:05.200
Tianci is the heir to my Ye family

4
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:06.366
He can't have an accident

5
00:00:06.466 --> 00:00:08.200
Young Master, you can't take the risk

6
00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:09.166
Stop talking

7
00:00:09.166 --> 00:00:10.100
I don't draw my sword

8
00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:11.500
You and your father will both die

9
00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:12.533
I don't draw my sword

10
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.766
So many people see me laughing

11
00:00:16.566 --> 00:00:17.500
I don't draw my sword

12
00:00:19.066 --> 00:00:20.566
Mengmeng will have an accident

13
00:00:20.633 --> 00:00:22.633
Look what we do

14
00:00:22.633 --> 00:00:24.400
Do you think we can save Mengmeng?

15
00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:25.766
Dream on.

16
00:00:25.866 --> 00:00:27.466
It's your own flesh and blood after all

17
00:00:27.466 --> 00:00:28.866
I have only one request

18
00:00:28.966 --> 00:00:30.100
If I lose my bones

19
00:00:30.100 --> 00:00:33.033
I only beg you to at least send Mengmeng to the orphanage

20
00:00:33.033 --> 00:00:34.600
Don't let him live on the streets

21
00:00:35.266 --> 00:00:37.266
Oops, why are you listening to him?

22
00:00:37.266 --> 00:00:39.066
If the child is gone, it can be regenerated.

23
00:00:39.066 --> 00:00:40.366
But the opportunity is gone

24
00:00:40.366 --> 00:00:42.766
Then it's really gone, sorry.

25
00:00:42.866 --> 00:00:43.966
I can't do it.

26
00:00:45.366 --> 00:00:47.733
Mom, don't you want me?

27
00:00:47.766 --> 00:00:48.766
Need a chance

28
00:00:48.766 --> 00:00:50.733
I need a chance to soar

29
00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:54.200
Mengmenglai

30
00:00:56.066 --> 00:00:58.000
Mengmeng, today we advance and retreat together

31
00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:59.833
Let's watch dad become a world-renowned hero together

32
00:00:59.833 --> 00:01:01.200
Okay? Okay?

33
00:01:01.433 --> 00:01:05.433
I'm a little security guard and a big hero

34
00:01:05.433 --> 00:01:06.966
There was no choice.

35
00:01:06.966 --> 00:01:09.000
Young Master, we believe in you

36
00:01:13.966 --> 00:01:14.800
Ye Tianci

37
00:01:15.800 --> 00:01:17.300
I have been with you for 5 years

38
00:01:17.300 --> 00:01:19.233
I know your virtues best

39
00:01:19.233 --> 00:01:22.133
Don't worry, if you pull it out, you'll be dead

40
00:01:22.233 --> 00:01:24.966
I suggest you just let it go

41
00:01:24.966 --> 00:01:26.333
He dare not pull it out

